<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,1661,1788]" pageId="1" pageNumber="585">
We do not present generic diagnosis since it is not informative. That is because genus 
<taxonomicName box="[1068,1179,1661,1684]" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Hedotettix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="585" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
